  "detailed_description": "<h1>WILL YOU ENJOY ARCSINE? WHAT TO KNOW BEFORE YOU BUY:</h1><p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong><u>ArcSine is a physically active standing experience - No smooth/snap turning</u></strong><br></li><li><strong><u>Get ready for a significant challenge</u></strong> - This game will push you hard<br></li><li><strong><u>Watch the trailer!</u></strong><br></li><li>Fast-paced, first-person, VR, single-player, linear, storyless, precision puzzle platforming<br></li><li>340+ stages with a huge variety of environment/movement mechanics<br></li><li>A sweeping & intricate electronic soundtrack<br></li><li>Motion-smoothed wide angle streaming mode<br></li><li>Instant respawns and stage loading<br></li><li>Leaderboards and real-time speedrunning stats</li></ul></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1869600/extras/85181b6fbf8e6113752fccb51c152853.poster.avif?t=1708352394\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1869600/extras/85181b6fbf8e6113752fccb51c152853.webm?t=1708352394\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1869600/extras/85181b6fbf8e6113752fccb51c152853.mp4?t=1708352394\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1869600/extras/c4c9aa62de85faf8a9eacba084b2f766.poster.avif?t=1708352394\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1869600/extras/c4c9aa62de85faf8a9eacba084b2f766.webm?t=1708352394\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop pl